title: RHOA: A Fashion Show WITH Fashions
itunes:title: RHOA: A Fashion Show WITH Fashions
description:
Danny recaps the finale of The Real Housewives of Atlanta, which featured closure, CVS, Dwight, and a fashion show complete with fashions! Danny also touches on seasonal body wash, Southern Charm, what he'll be like as a ghost, and more!
